.SH NAME
cert-ski - Display Subject Key Identifier (SKI) for keys/certs


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcert ski [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Display the Subject Key Identifier (SKI) for one or more keys or
certificates. Note that this does not support remote certificates.

.PP
When multiple files are provided with --should-match, all SKIs
are compared and a warning is printed if any differ. The output includes the
input path, SKI, key type, and file type.

.PP
Use --display-mode to control hex formatting of the SKI (default: lower).


.SH OPTIONS
